        <div class="card-detail" style="height:200px; text-align: justify-all; overflow-y:auto;">
                The downstairs area of our house is self-contained accommodation. It has a large bedroom, small kitchenette, small bathroom - shower basin and toilet, and modest living area with TV.
                The bedroom is large and has a Queen size bed and there is a sofa that converts to another double bed. Comfortable for two people and maybe two additional little ones. There is a chest of drawers, wardrobe and bedside cabinets and lights, and a small bookcase.
            Laundry is at the back of the garage where there is a laundry tub and all-in-one washing machine-dryer.
                While the Downstairs of our house is for your sole use while you are here, there are some areas that are shared access. The front entrance is shared, assess to the garage is shared. There are storage cupboards and an area under the stairs we regard as shared access.
                Our car is normally parked in the garage, so the garage is not available, nor is parking in front of the garage. If the RVPark is not occupied, then that may be available, or a car can be parked in front of the front door.
                Keyless access is via the garage door and the key to the front door is inside.
                Pets: No pets inside sorry.
                There is a small kitchenette with fridge freezer, microwave, air-fryer, one-pot hotplate, instant pot,  jug, toaster, coffee gear - filter and plunger. The microwave has several other cooking modes, and the manual is close by.
            Bathroom is small with toilet, shower, and basin. There is a bit of a step up to the shower base. 
                And finally, the living area has a 2-seater couch, small table and two chairs, and TV with internet access. No Sky at this stage but multi room (without sports) may be available in time.<br/>
